                    "><strong>Moroccans protested in Rabat against Israel’s military campaign in Gaza and US support for the war</strong>. In one of the largest demonstrations in months, the protestors condemned the ethnic cleansing of Gaza and the normalization of ties with Israel through the Abraham Accords. There have also been rallies across the Middle East and North Africa, including Tunisia and Yemen (<a style="text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 2px solid  #4D3060; color: black;" href="https://link.presidentialsummary.com/ps-08-04-2025-br1-7-the-background" target="_blank">the background</a>).</p>
                    
