              font-size: 16px;
              line-height: 1.5;
              border-left: 3px solid #4D3060;
              padding-left: 14px;
              margin-bottom: 15px;
                    "><strong>The EU has proposed a 25% counter-tariff on US goods such as diamonds, eggs, and poultry</strong> in retaliation for Trump’s steel and aluminum tariffs. Some of these tariffs take effect on May 16, while others will begin on December 1. Items like bourbon and wine were removed to steer away from escalation. EU countries will vote on the proposal on April 9 (<a style="text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 2px solid  #4D3060; color: black;" href="https://link.presidentialsummary.com/ps-08-04-2025-br4-10-eu-offensive" target="_blank">EU offensive</a>).</p>
